 can enhance valley splitting and $d_{11}$ (absolute\nvalue). The predicted Curie temperature of YBrI is higher than those of\nexperimentally synthesized 2D ferromagnetic materials $\\mathrm{CrI_3}$ and\n$\\mathrm{Cr_2Ge_2Te_6}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2022 02:53:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-04"}
