oS-psi method leads to inaccuracies that are mostly\ncorrected by the VoS-psi' formulation. In addition, the VoS methods are\nsignificantly faster than the ALE method, with a speed-up factor of between 2\nand 12.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2022 15:14:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-15"}
